name: PlugMusic Presents 'Plug Pixel Keyboard'- Mix & Mastering Services #029
description:
These are a special utility NFT that offer Mix & Mastering services from where ever you are in the world using collaborated Renowned Music Engineers.
Owning this NFT entitles you to membership to various community groups and other promotional services in the future.
This collection was inspired by Tandra' and and hand drawn by Lord Plug.
There are only 40 individual unique 'Plug Pixel Keyboards' in this collection.
Please send all information once purchased to: info@plugworld.io to redeem services.
